{"tid":1835534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］蘋果日報：沙士15 - 聽我講","createTime":"2020-01-23T01:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:13:06.000Z","uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9fd5caf3f366360f7fd12bce9e789b2342ba614","tid":1835534,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10158536384457448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10158536384457448&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fcbbb7f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10158536384457448</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/preamble/preamble_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2Fpreamble%2Fpreamble_title&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=15f4503c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2Fpreamble%2Fpreamble_title&h=4713cd43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/preamble/preamble_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n// 武漢肺炎疫情席捲全球，喚起了香港人對衛生的警覺性，也喚起了香港人一段悲痛無比的回憶。病源疑為「野味」、企圖淡化疫情、病毒擴散爆發，一幕幕不堪回首的畫面彷彿正在重播。<br />\n<br />\n03年「沙士」肆虐，阻隔了我們擁抱的衝動，更讓我們失去了299條性命，包括8位抗疫英雄。<br />\n我們絕不能忘記那段日子，也絕不能重蹈覆辙。2018年時值15週年，當時《蘋果》製作了沙士15周年專題網站，今天讓我們再一次揭到過去的那一頁，透過歷史去警惕今天的你、我和「他們」。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，提提大家：「千祈千祈千祈，洗手洗手洗手」"},{"pid":"587a00f97f1175ecdc427e1ca269bd155549e53a","tid":1835534,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}